 and iron-handed rule come up against profound resilience of spirit, expatriate life ambles along, and nongovernmental organizations struggle with the risk of co-option by the military junta.Burma Chronicles is drawn with a minimal line, and interspersed with wordless vignettes and moments of Delisle's distinctive slapstick humor.</i></p>]]></description><first_appearance_characters><character><api_detail_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/api/character/4005-128788/]]></api_detail_url><id>128788</id><name><![CDATA[Guy Delisle]]></name><site_detail_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/guy-delisle/4005-128788/]]></site_detail_url></character></first_appearance_characters><first_appearance_concepts><concept><api_detail_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/api/concept/4015-55924/]]></api_detail_url><id>55924</id><name><![CDATA[Real World Stories]]></name><site_detail_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/real-world-stories/4015-55924/]]></site_detail_url></concept></first_appearance_concepts><first_appearance_locations><location><api_detail_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/api/location/4020-55797/]]></api_detail_url><id>55797</id><name><![CDATA[Burma]]></name><site_detail_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/burma/4020-55797/]]></site_detail_url></location></first_appearance_locations><first_appearance_objects/><first_appearance_storyarcs/><first_appearance_teams/><has_staff_review></has_staff_review><id>314533</id><image><icon_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/api/image/square_avatar/2436624-burmachronicles.jpg]]></icon_url><medium_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/api/image/scale_medium/2436624-burmachronicles.jpg]]></medium_url><screen_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/api/image/screen_medium/2436624-burmachronicles.jpg]]></screen_url><small_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamespot.com/api/image/scale_small/2436624-burmachronicles.jpg]]></small_url><super_url><![CDATA[https://comicvine.gamesp